cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper proposes a method to accelerate feedforward computations, which is a common task in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses solving a system of nonlinear equations using fixed-point iteration methods, which falls under the category of numerical analysis (cs.NA). The experiments involve evaluating DenseNets on ImageNet (cs.CV - Computer Vision) and autoregressive sampling of MADE and PixelCNN (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also discusses parallel computing, which is relevant to distributed systems (cs.DS).
